Package org.apparatus_templi.xml

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ElementInterface
    An interface for all objects which can automatically generate their own XML representation data.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Button
    Represents a button to render in the widget or full page XML data.
    Controller
    A representation of a controller located in a remote module.
    InputType
    A convenience class that contains a list of known valid Button input types.
    Pre
    An element that holds pre-formatted HTML.
    Sensor
    A representation of a sensor in a remote module.
    TextArea
    An Element to hold a line of text.
    XmlFormatter
    A convenience class to handle generating XML data that conforms to the schema for full page XML and widget XML data.
